@node Future "Future"
Future versions of ANSIshell will hopefully do/have the following:

 - Allow argument of which font & size to be used
 - Allow argument of which screenmode to be used

Any other suggestions? If people ask me to update it, then I will,
but because I need no other functions, I won't update it if people
aren't using it.
@endnode
